### REGISTER USER
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Puish",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "puishuser@gmail.com",
  "password": "Puish@123",
  "role": "USER"
}

### LOGIN AS ADMIN (admin is auto-seeded in DB)
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@taskmanager.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### LOGIN AS USER
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "puishuser@gmail.com",
  "password": "Puish@123"
}

### LOGOUT
GET http://localhost:5000/auth/logout

### GET ALL USERS (Admin only - login as admin first)
GET http://localhost:5000/user-api/users

### GET SINGLE USER (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/user-api/users/USER_ID_HERE

### TOGGLE USER ACTIVE STATUS (Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/user-api/users/USER_ID_HERE/toggle-active

### DELETE USER (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/user-api/users/USER_ID_HERE